nodes.text: Imperial Works Project 900316A was a reconstituted Sith Empire project that Captain Guyvar was involved with on Dromund Kaas.

Imperial Works Project 900316A was originally detailed in a cut mission in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, which identified the project as an ecological studies crew manned by Chevin workers. The mission was cut from the game before release, but Guyvar still mentions the name of the project when clicked on.
